In this lab exercise I created a program that will take input from the user then sort and display the names in alphabetical order.

Then it will prompt the user to input a name they'd like to search, and display the position of that name.

While simple, this program helped me to lay foundational practice on using public classes and taking input variable from the user
and it helped my knowledge to grow on error checking to quit the program when the user attempts to input anything other 
than the prompted text.
